window.bookSummaryJSON = "<i>They're out there....</i> <br>Waiting. Watching. Unseen by normal eyes, but all too visible to Slim MacKenzie, a young man blessed - or cursed - by Twilight Eyes. <p><i>They're out there....</i><br>Lurking in the darkest shadows of an eerie, moonlit carnival. Feeding their twisted needs with human suffering - and fiendishly plotting the downfall of the human race.</p> <p><i>They're out there....</i><br>But don't scream. They'll hear you.</p>"; 
